These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up, mirinda
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, golf, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is golf is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | milk | 7up | mirinda   |
| Sport      | tennis    | golf  | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, soy-milk
There are 3 different nationalities: thai, colombian, indian
1. the thai is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the colombian is on the far left##1
3. the colombian is the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | sprite | cola     | soy-milk      |
| Nationality   | colombian | thai | indian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, 7up
There 3 different types of food: potato, asparagus, pear
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person eating pear##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | cola | 7up  | iced-tea       |
| Food       | potato     | asparagus | pear |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, lettuce, watermelon
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, collecting, magic-tricks
1. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person eating kale is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | watermelon    | lettuce     | kale |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | hiking | collecting     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: rat, frog, fish
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, motorbike, car
1. the person driving the motorbike is the owner of the fish##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
3. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the owner of the rat is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | frog | rat     | fish |
| Transport   | car        | taxi | motorbike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, pepper, cucumber
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, ship, jet-ski
1. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person driving the car##1
2. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
3. the person eating cucumber is the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | cucumber | broccoli      | pepper  |
| Transport   | car       | ship | jet-ski |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, trance, metal
3 different pets are kept: hamster, snake, turtle
1. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of rock##1
2. the fan of trance is the owner of the snake##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | metal      | rock     | trance    |
| Pet           | hamster | turtle | snake |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
