2. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person eating papaya is the person who's hobby is cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food    | kiwi | orange | papaya      |
| Hobby   | writing     | woodworking | cooking |

