.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, milk, coffee
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, martial-arts, sports
1. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | water   | milk    | coffee    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | epic | sports |

