.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-19::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, woodworking, photography
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, classical, dubstep
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the fan of dubstep##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby         | card-games | woodworking | photography |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | dubstep     | classical  |

