.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, watermelon, apple
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, parkour, sailing
1. the person who's sport is parkour is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
3. the person eating watermelon is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | apple | raspberry       | watermelon  |
| Sport   | sailing  | parkour | baseball |

 